      <title>vue前端学习和element-UI框架的基础使用</title>
      <link href="/2019/09/18/20190918/"/>
      <url>/2019/09/18/20190918/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>问题描述：el-table 表格合并，第二行多列进行合并，并且合计金额等数据</p><p>解决方法：拿到table数据list之后，将合计total unshift到list数组里面，这样就能实现合计在表格的第一行</p><p><code>代码</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//table 对应的label和value值 循环打印</span><br><span class="line">&lt;el-table-column</span><br><span class="line">v-for=&quot;(item.index) in tableList&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :key=&quot;index&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :prop=&quot;item.prop&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  :label=&quot;item.label&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  width=&quot;180&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">&lt;/el-table-column&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>所以问题出现了，这样循环打印出来的table，里面的第二行是无法添加合计值的，</p><p>所以最后合计的值是需要将unshift到tableList里面去。这样第一行就可以输出在第一行了</p><p><code>代码</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//第一行合并，需要用到span-method方法：arraySpanMethod</span><br><span class="line">arraySpanMethod(&#123;row,column,rowIndex,columnIndex&#125;)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">if(rowIndex == 0)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">if(columnIndex == 0)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">return [1,4]//第一行的前四列都设置为合计</span><br><span class="line">&#125;else if(columnIndex &gt; 0 &amp;&amp; columnIndex &lt; 4)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">return [0,0]   //表示在第一行的第二到第四列都合并</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>因为这样的想法只是在理论上实现了，而自己的项目上还没有实现，所以有待接下来的更新。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
